text: {| |} USNS Cody (T-EPF-14) will be the fourteenth and will be operated by the Military Sealift Command. It will be the first ship in naval service named after Cody, Wyoming. ==References== Category:Transports of the United States Navy Category:Ships built in Mobile, Alabama Category:Spearhead-class Joint High Speed Vessels
title: USNS Cody
